comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_uyd" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/smoofra/">smoofra</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">15 June 2009 03:49:24PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_uyd'>7 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_uyd'] = ['6 points', '7 points', '8 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_uyd')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_uyd" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>"I don't, I've come to believe, have to agree with you to like you, or respect you."</p>

