ng.com/user/hrishimittal/">hrishimittal</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">16 June 2009 02:32:51AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_v24'>5 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_v24'] = ['4 points', '5 points', '6 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_v24')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_v24" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>It reminds me very much of this quote attributed to Gautam Buddha:</p>

