" onclick="return showcomment('t1_uwz')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_uwz" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_uwz" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Stefan_King/">Stefan_King</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">15 June 2009 09:17:46AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_uwz'>7 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_uwz'] = ['6 points', '7 points', '8 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_uwz')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_uwz" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
