="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_uxb')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_uxb" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>It is ridiculous, silly to watch and excruciatingly embarrassing to perform when sober.</p>
</blockquote>

